data.description: Introducing a splendid residence nestled in the heart of the meticulously maintained community of Oaks Devonshire. This stunning, newly listed home boasts five spacious bedrooms, three full baths, plus a convenient half bathroom. As you step into this haven, you'll be greeted by an inviting open concept layout, highlighted by a generously proportioned kitchen that seamlessly flows into the living spaces, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying family gatherings.    Step outside to unveil the enchanting highlight of this property - a vast, meticulously landscaped backyard. This outdoor paradise provides plenty of room for outdoor activities, relaxation, and the potential for creating your personalized outdoor oasis.    Situated in the sought-after Oaks Devonshire community, this home embodies a serene neighborhood feel while providing convenient access to local amenities, schools, and parks. It’s the perfect harmony of comfortable living in a well-kept and vibrant community.
